page.title: 01HOME LIFE REDDITCH
page.content: THERE ARE MOST OF THE DIFFERENT TYPES OF HOUSING IN OUR PART OF{REDDITCH,} THERE ARE DETACHED HOUSES,SEMI-DETACHED,TERRACED HOUSES, AND FLATS.MY NAME IS {VIKKI,}I LIVE WITH MY MUM AND DAD AND TWO SISTERS,I HAVE ONE PET, A CAT CALLED SNOWDROP.THERE ARE FOUR BEDROOMS IN MY HOUSE,AN ATTIC TO STORE THINGS, THERE IS ALSO A BATHROOM, AND SHOWER.DOWNSTAIRS THERE IS A KITCHEN,A LOUNGE, AND A HALL.WHEN I AM AT HOME I PLAY WITH MY SISTERS,WE SOMETIMES PLAY IN THE PARK NEAR MY HOUSE.MY FATHER GOES OUT TO WORK AS AN ENGINEER,AND MY MOTHER IS A MERCHANDISER.
